article_id:1260,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding an Issue with First Clear Rewards for a Certain Quest,image_path:,message:<div>An error that caused the number of Great Feathers obtained as first clear rewards to display as zero and making it impossible to obtain them occurred between <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1587362400"></span> and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1587708000"></span> in main campaign Ch. 13 / 4-2, which was added <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1587362400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>This issue was fixed as described below in a data update at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1587708000"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Before correction: Great Feathers x0</div><div>After correction: Great Feathers x3</div><div><br></div><div>Players who encountered this issue will be sent the materials they should have received.</div><div><br></div><div>These items can be collected from your goodie box.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1587708000,update_time1587702364